[I] Scripts and setting files useful during development of KDE software

[T] KDE Dev Scripts is a collection of utility scripts designed to assist
[T] developers working on KDE projects. These scripts are meant to simplify
[T] common development tasks specific to KDE's infrastructure and development
[T] practice.

